{"TopicId":149533,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Science fiction authors of the KSP forums, UNITE!","CreatedByName":"Spaceception","CreatedById":152800,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-09T01:52:30Z","PageNum":10,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"AlbertKermin","CreatedById":110967,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-19T09:48:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI actually just published a sci-fi novella, so I thought I\u0027d share. It details the adventures of the astronauts on the first manned mission to titan, as told by one of them through her blog.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s also partly inspired by a Laythe mission I ran back in the KSP 0.23.5 days.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07FP4VGFS\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.amazon.com/dp/B07FP4VGFS\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:9px;\u0022\u003EI am aware that spell-check pulled a fast one on me in the Amazon description. It should be fixed shortly.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-07-19T10:17:27Z\u0022 title=\u002207/19/2018 10:17  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 19, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by AlbertKermin\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-06T03:06:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI heff arrived.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Piatzin","CreatedById":166940,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-06T05:51:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223446069\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149533\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221536203191\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160817\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lo Var Lachland\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Lo Var Lachland said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI heff arrived.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGrootings, ferwrorw writer\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-06T20:34:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223446129\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149533\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221536213076\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022166940\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Earthlinger\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, Earthlinger said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGrootings, ferwrorw writer\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHewwo fellow human. I come in peace.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DAL59","CreatedById":180784,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-08T01:51:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223417401\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149533\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221531882871\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022127797\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bill Phil\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/17/2018 at 11:01 PM, Bill Phil said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis gives me an idea...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat if we had a kind of fantasy world, that was realistic. We could have a whole \u0022Lord of the Rings\u0022 style thing happen, and then a big reveal that the world is actually a generation ship on a thousand year journey\u00A0to... say... Trappist-1 (why not?).\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProbably not a new idea, but then again, what is?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr have a computer simulation\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-08T08:23:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am so hyped for the plot of my current story,\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/168215-we-who-witnessed-chapter-v-rift/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EWe Who Witnessed.\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0I think its going to be the best novel I\u0027ve ever written. If you don\u0027t have time to read the whole thing, just skim through the description at the top and tell me what you think. I am really enjoying writing this, and I hope people like reading it, too.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Piatzin","CreatedById":166940,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-08T15:43:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223447311\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149533\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221536395012\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160817\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lo Var Lachland\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Lo Var Lachland said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0I think its going to be the best novel I\u0027ve ever written.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWait, how many novels have you even written?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve spent two years on one and it\u0027s barely ~80% done\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-08T21:50:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223447496\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149533\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221536421393\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022166940\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Earthlinger\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Earthlinger said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWait, how many novels have you even written?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve spent two years on one and it\u0027s barely ~80% done\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA few, actually. As well as some short-stories, poems, and other shtuff.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Piatzin","CreatedById":166940,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-08T21:52:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223447681\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149533\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221536443411\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160817\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lo Var Lachland\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Lo Var Lachland said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA few, actually\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFull-length?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKudos regardless though \u003Cspan\u003E:D\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bill Phil","CreatedById":127797,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-10T02:11:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do have an idea for a KSP story...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI need to work it out though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DAL59","CreatedById":180784,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-23T03:55:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-002-ex\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-002-ex\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo many ideas\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-23T14:27:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223417401\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149533\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221531882871\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022127797\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bill Phil\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/18/2018 at 5:01 AM, Bill Phil said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis gives me an idea...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat if we had a kind of fantasy world, that was realistic. We could have a whole \u0022Lord of the Rings\u0022 style thing happen, and then a big reveal that the world is actually a generation ship on a thousand year journey\u00A0to... say... Trappist-1 (why not?).\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProbably not a new idea, but then again, what is?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSpeaking of realistic fantasy worlds, i recently played with the idea of having a fantasy world with creatures like Ogres and Dragons, but have them have some sort of evolutionary timeline and stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRight now im thinking of a future space colonization scenario were the first space war will take place, so i can kind of get an idea what a space war will be like, rather than just make something up in the middle of it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}